strings: <voice_0x01000C8F><se_def>Legal!: The moon has grown many times since humans last walked the earth. Welcome to Moonshade, a weary traveller.
<voice_0x01000C90><se_def>Legal!: Tell me, what Yueying wants to order you today? Needless to say, shoes tell stories.
<voice_0x01000C91><se_def>Legal!: ... that's why Pavan wants to see his beloved Sasha again.
<voice_0x01000C92><se_def>Legal!: You stand with your mouth open and empty. Sorry, I haven't woken up yet.
<voice_0x01000C93><se_def>Legal!: Guys these days...do you think your memory is yours alone?
<voice_0x01000C94><se_def>Legal!: Your clothes, your house, your table, your chair... the world... also reminds us of that past.
<voice_0x01000C95><se_def>Legal!: They sleep peacefully in a dream world full of memories.
<voice_0x01000C97><se_def>Legal!: You may not be able to wake the Sun Princess from her slumber, but you can stop your friend's waking nightmare.
<voice_0x01000C98><se_def>Legal!: Take me to the palace, take me to the edge of the palace
